Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.03,0:00:13.11,DTB-Default,Corinna,0,0,0,,Do you believe in the urban legend?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:18.23,DTB-Default,Corinna,0,0,0,,You can retrieve what you once lost inside the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.23,0:00:21.52,DTB-Default,Corinna,0,0,0,,However, it comes at a substantial price.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.51,0:00:24.54,DTB-Default,Corinna,0,0,0,,I wonder what that price is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.55,0:00:27.42,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.45,0:00:31.74,DTB-Default,Corinna,0,0,0,,You don't believe me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.45,0:00:34.83,DTB-Default,Corinna,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, neither do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.19,0:00:40.14,DTB-Default,Corinna,0,0,0,,I'm Corinna Moku, a third-year student at Beijing University.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.58,0:00:42.02,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I'm Li Shun Sheng.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.49,0:00:43.51,DTB-Default,Corinna,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:05.15,DTB-Default,Corinna,0,0,0,,It's larger than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.25,0:01:41.39,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Infiltrate PANDORA's research facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:43.98,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.98,0:01:46.39,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,It's right by the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.39,0:01:50.67,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,If a contractor goes near a hot spot, he might lose control.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.26,0:01:52.71,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:57.36,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Besides, I don't think he'll be able to pass the initial security check.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.87,0:02:00.00,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,That might be true, but the syndicate is serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.47,0:02:02.62,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,What do they want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:04.24,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Retrieval.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.24,0:02:06.00,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Retrieval?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.51,0:02:10.43,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Two weeks ago, there was an incident involving an explosion at the research facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:14.31,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Two security guards were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.83,0:02:21.41,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,PANDORA, responsible for the investigation, concluded that it was a structural accident caused by faulty wiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.13,0:02:28.92,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,A few days ago, a covert CIA agent discovered that the explosion was intentionally triggered
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:34.33,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,in order to steal the gate-proprietary substance referred to as the "meteor fragment".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.59,0:02:39.61,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,It still hasn't been transported outside of the wall, has it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.61,0:02:41.99,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,That's how the syndicate sees the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:44.28,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,What's to be done after the retrieval?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.63,0:02:47.93,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,You're to transport it out of the gate in their place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:50.29,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.92,0:03:04.93,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Just do as you're told.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:06.93,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,It's just business as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:11.15,DTB-Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,Do you consider yourself a patient person?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:12.43,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:15.52,DTB-Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,Have you ever seen a UFO?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.94,0:03:16.85,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:19.44,DTB-Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,Do you believe in the existence of God?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:20.77,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.21,0:03:23.08,DTB-Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,Do you know any contractors?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.94,0:03:24.90,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.72,0:03:41.38,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Um, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.85,0:03:45.26,DTB-Default,Corinna,0,0,0,,N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.99,0:03:53.27,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Um, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.27,0:03:55.27,DTB-Default,Corinna,0,0,0,,Didn't I already say everything was fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.52,0:04:00.80,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:01.90,DTB-Default,Kirk,0,0,0,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.36,0:04:07.84,DTB-Default,Corinna,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.28,0:04:09.40,DTB-Default,Controller,0,0,0,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:14.67,DTB-Default,Kirk,0,0,0,,You're coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:16.67,DTB-Default,Corinna,0,0,0,,No, let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:18.62,DTB-Default,Corinna,0,0,0,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:23.92,DTB-Default,Kirk,0,0,0,,Take her back to testing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.09,0:04:31.01,DTB-Default,Controller,0,0,0,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:34.45,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.29,0:04:47.66,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,Ghosts aren't a rare sight in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:51.71,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,Things that exist tend to disappear, while things that don't tend to appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:54.75,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,Auditory hallucinations and similar occurrences aren't out of the ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:58.28,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,You won't get the job done if you lose composure whenever it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.28,0:05:07.75,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,Besides, world-renowned scientists are working day and night to solve similar supernatural phenomena in this facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.15,0:05:14.39,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,Our job is to provide an optimal working environment for them, which isn't an easy thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.39,0:05:21.15,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,In any case, you guys aren't allowed to leave this place for the next month without exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:23.73,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,Even if you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:27.53,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,If you get the message, answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:28.75,DTB-Default,Men,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:32.10,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,This is Sector Three,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:36.87,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,the most important area we're responsible for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:41.48,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,Standard cleaning duties occur late at night, when research isn't being conducted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.00,0:05:47.03,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:51.01,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.44,0:05:56.91,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,You don't need to clean that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.26,0:05:58.53,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:02.46,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,The man in charge of that room is notoriously meticulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:03.59,DTB-Default,Sergei,0,0,0,,Gentlemen...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.41,0:06:06.36,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,Chief Sergei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:08.43,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,Hey! Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.93,0:06:21.51,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,You idiot! What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:23.34,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:26.20,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,Why are you just standing there? Hurry and pick it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.77,0:06:27.55,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:29.68,DTB-Default,Sergei,0,0,0,,I'll be going ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:31.12,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:40.94,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:43.28,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,I hope you're not hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.28,0:06:45.03,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,Yes. Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:52.58,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:53.98,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,We're off to the next one!
