Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.07,0:07:01.75,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,How did you know it was me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:06.40,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,I knew they were sending someone to the sanitation division.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:09.36,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Is there anyone else from the syndicate?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:13.12,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,Yes, but I've never met them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.77,0:07:14.75,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,0:07:18.01,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,Listen, I want to tell you something in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:20.27,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,Don't rely on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:25.80,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,I only cooperate with the syndicate so I can conduct research here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.15,0:07:28.34,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,It's the first time I've done this kind of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.73,0:07:31.94,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,There wasn't any occurrence for two years, and suddenly this happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:35.89,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Rest assured. I won't rely on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.38,0:07:40.54,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,That aside, I want to ask you about the meteor fragment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:44.00,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:46.04,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Tell me everything you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.56,0:07:51.19,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,To be honest, the details are unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.02,0:07:57.24,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,However, a similar substance was confirmed before the disappearance of South America,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:08:03.96,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,so it's believed that collecting data on it will be invaluable when it comes to solving the mystery behind the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:10.45,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,I don't know why the CIA is trying to steal it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.53,0:08:14.49,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,This isn't part of the job, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:18.78,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,Excuse me. If anything else comes up, I'll contact you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:30.24,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,Sorry for the late introduction. My name is Mina Khandar Swami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:34.94,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,By the way, that sticker doesn't serve much of a purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:39.76,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,There isn't any way to identify a contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:12.89,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Don't touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:16.21,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,I'm in the middle of an experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:20.96,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,I thought my instructions explicitly stated not to have this room cleaned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:26.22,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I noticed it was the same model as the one I used to have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.22,0:09:27.72,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Satake?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.72,0:09:29.72,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Do you also gaze at the stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:33.59,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I did before the stars became what they are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:35.74,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:37.68,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Li Shun Sheng.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.33,0:09:39.52,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Li-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.52,0:09:40.32,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.03,0:09:47.21,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,How would you like to see a real star?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:52.59,Title,,0,0,0,,Episode Eleven When One Takes Back What Was Lost Within the Wall... (Part One)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:59.14,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Satake may be new as a domestic manufacturer,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:02.30,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,but their products come equipped with an inexpensive, high-performance lens.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:06.68,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,There are limits to the magnifying capabilities of an ML800, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.10,0:10:09.10,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Did you use a Barlow lens?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:12.85,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,No. Compatible lenses were too expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.85,0:10:17.13,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,I see. Your wishes will be answered in ten years time, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.93,0:10:21.14,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Um... What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:24.44,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,I'm looking at the stars. What else would I be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:26.12,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.84,0:10:30.75,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Are you going to give up because you know the sky is just a fabrication?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.24,0:10:32.64,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:37.18,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,My entire life changed when this sky appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.15,0:10:43.67,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,I don't have any intention of giving up this hobby of mine, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:46.60,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,You should take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:01.67,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I can't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.29,0:11:04.27,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Forget about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:06.54,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Forget that the moon has vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.01,0:11:12.51,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Forget about all the rockets that have gone missing beyond the stratosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.87,0:11:20.44,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,You have to believe that these stars are the ones you were gazing at in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.24,0:11:36.53,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.53,0:11:38.38,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,There was nothing there a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.69,0:11:42.86,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,We're within the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.86,0:11:47.85,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,"The impossible becomes possible" is the best explanation I can come up with at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:50.58,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,The explanation is a little subpar coming from a scientist, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:59.51,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,I can assert that what you've witnessed is the beginning of a likely scenario for the future of this planet, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.87,0:12:06.85,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Li-kun, what do you think will happen if everyone in the world experiences what we just did?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:15.25,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,I have a feeling we'll regain a genuine starry sky when that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:21.53,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,You're an honest person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:23.87,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Your facial expression says "no way".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:27.80,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Well, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:31.76,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,You should join our group someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:35.80,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,It only consists of my sister and me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:37.33,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.33,0:12:41.19,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Yeah. She can't move her appendages right now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:42.72,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,If only for a day,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:48.20,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,I want to remove this fabricated sky and take her into outer space.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.98,0:12:50.93,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,That's my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:56.33,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,That dream... I hope it becomes a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:00.73,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:15.51,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,May I sit here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:24.99,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Is everything all right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.19,0:13:27.93,DTB-Default,Corinna,0,0,0,,I can see things that I've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.49,0:13:31.23,DTB-Default,Corinna,0,0,0,,Two, three...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:32.64,DTB-Default,Corinna,0,0,0,,Everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:37.04,DTB-Default,Corinna,0,0,0,,I've decided to leave this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:39.06,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Leave? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:43.02,DTB-Default,Corinna,0,0,0,,If I hand it to that man, I'll be able to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.94,0:13:46.63,DTB-Default,Corinna,0,0,0,,I told you it's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:48.60,DTB-Default,Corinna,0,0,0,,How long are you going to chase me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.60,0:13:50.49,DTB-Default,Corinna,0,0,0,,You're already dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:54.98,DTB-Default,Corinna,0,0,0,,Whether I betray the country or Mama, I won't take any more of this from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:59.66,DTB-Default,Corinna,0,0,0,,I am who I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.72,0:14:07.07,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,If you go that far, it might be difficult to return to society.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.51,0:14:11.08,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,She's thinking about leaving this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:12.93,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Without waiting a month?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:14.29,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:17.21,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:18.81,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:20.61,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,That's a cause for concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:32.83,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.83,0:15:37.30,DTB-Default,Colleague,0,0,0,,That crazy woman named Corinna was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:40.25,DTB-Default,Colleague,0,0,0,,The security camera was out of order when it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:43.63,DTB-Default,Kirk,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:46.42,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,Yes, I saw it with my very own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.89,0:15:48.11,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,It's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:55.67,DTB-Default,Kirk,0,0,0,,I heard you two were close.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.44,0:16:00.44,DTB-Default,Kirk,0,0,0,,Too many improbable occurrences have taken place here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,0:16:07.32,DTB-Default,Kirk,0,0,0,,For example, a crime of passion involving two people who just met each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:13.20,DTB-Default,Kirk,0,0,0,,Did she tell you anything before she was killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.25,0:16:15.63,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.53,0:16:35.35,DTB-Default,Kirk,0,0,0,,Keep an eye on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.35,0:16:36.46,DTB-Default,Kikuchi,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.63,0:16:44.64,DTB-Default,Kirk,0,0,0,,Yes, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:47.55,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,Was it really not you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.18,0:16:49.77,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I had no reason to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.51,0:16:52.48,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,Do you need one,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.48,0:16:56.09,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,even if you're a contractor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:57.60,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Is that all you had to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:17:00.12,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,If you have no further business...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:04.64,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,Could you be... upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:10.58,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:14.43,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,I thought contractors were people who lost their emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:19.76,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,If you didn't do it, then who...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.20,0:17:27.98,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,There I go again. I'm sorry, I was out of line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.67,0:17:31.32,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,You can make all the assumptions you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:34.48,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,but don't act on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.48,0:17:38.55,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,That is... If you want to continue with your research. Is that clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:40.59,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:45.41,DTB-Default,Kirk,0,0,0,,The female victim was a courier sent by the CIA.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.76,0:17:51.94,DTB-Default,Kirk,0,0,0,,She was planning on handing us the meteor fragment in exchange for her release from the facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:56.19,DTB-Default,Kirk,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, she didn't mention its location.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:59.49,DTB-Default,Kirk,0,0,0,,I understand. I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.88,0:18:11.74,DTB-Default,Announcement,0,0,0,,We will now commence an area search using the surveillance camera operated by Dr. Sergei's Third Sector team.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.74,0:18:15.64,DTB-Default,Announcement,0,0,0,,All personnel with corresponding ID numbers, please proceed to Conference Room Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.54,0:18:23.76,DTB-Default,Sergei,0,0,0,,Within the premises, a phenomenon observed by different people will result in a myriad of experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:29.64,DTB-Default,Sergei,0,0,0,,The reason I asked you to come here is to gather as much observational data as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:35.68,DTB-Default,Sergei,0,0,0,,Let me know exactly what you see, hear, and feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:34.15,DTB-Overlap,Nick,0,0,0,,The interrogation must have been tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.65,0:18:36.11,DTB-Overlap,Li,0,0,0,,Nick-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:39.32,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,I know the feeling. I've experienced it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:42.86,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'm on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.86,0:18:45.39,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,You're not the type of person that can kill people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.51,0:18:51.01,DTB-Default,Sergei,0,0,0,,It's time. Begin the search.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:03.41,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,The surveillance camera is now in motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.63,0:19:16.44,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,It will soon pass Chiyoda Ward, Kanda 3-chome, and head toward Chuo-dori Avenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:20.94,DTB-Default,Sergei,0,0,0,,Stop it right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.36,0:19:25.46,DTB-Default,Sergei,0,0,0,,Can you zoom in just beyond that car?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.34,0:19:42.46,DTB-Default,Sergei,0,0,0,,It looks like we'll have to rewrite the map again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.02,0:19:45.54,DTB-Default,Sergei,0,0,0,,Return and travel on the west route.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:18.66,DTB-Default,Sergei,0,0,0,,Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.66,0:20:20.61,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,Yes, definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:21.59,DTB-Default,Sergei,0,0,0,,Right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.59,0:20:24.51,DTB-Default,Sergei,0,0,0,,Play it in slow motion from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.76,0:20:27.72,DTB-Default,Sergei,0,0,0,,Right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.06,0:20:31.10,DTB-Default,Mina,0,0,0,,Lancernopt synchrotron radiation?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:34.73,DTB-Default,Nick,0,0,0,,My, my... This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.81,0:20:37.64,DTB-Default,Sergei,0,0,0,,The meteor fragment?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.25,0:20:45.21,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Within the gate, you can retrieve what you once lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:51.54,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,What was seen inside the green mist was either a demon or a cursed remnant from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:56.76,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The irrevocable past is a bloody memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.76,0:21:01.95,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The starry sky that disappeared beyond the mirror is the one I saw with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:05.35,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Contractors do not dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:09.34,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,540)}Episode Twelve When One Takes Back What Was Lost Within the Wall... (Part Two)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.35,0:21:08.35,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The remuneration is complete.